dataset.description: Scott County building permit data represents permit data that is created and maintained by the Property and Taxation Services department.  This permit data represents permits that are issued on or after January 1, 2010, within a township, and that have a status of Finalled, Issued, or Expired.  Scott County is the permitting authority for the townships, to obtain permit data for a city within Scott County please contact the city. Once data has been downloaded and opened in Excel, you must select the dateIssued field and change the field type to Short Date or Long Date.

dataset.description:
2040 Comprehensive Land Use Plan for Scott County. For more information, please visit Scott County's 2040 Comprehensive Plan Implementation webpage: https://www.scottcountymn.gov/439/2040-Comprehensive-Plan

Comprehensive Plan data falls into 1 of 12 categories: Agricultural Preservation, Urban Expansion, Transition Area, Rural Residential Reserve, Rural Residential Growth, Park/Open Space, Commercial, Industrial, Rural Business Reserve, Urban Business Reserve, Hamlet Mixed Use Overlay, Areas Not Under County Planning Authority.
dataset.title: Comprehensive Landuse 2040
